Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no experience\Nwhen it comes to romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I have always been dense\Nwhen it comes to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As dense as I am, seeing her tears\Nwere enough to make me realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized what Shichimiya\Nhad been attempting to make war with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why she asked me those questions,\Nand why she made me say those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.51,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The water mage's\Nattack has intensified.\NRescue requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why she wept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New discovery. I would like to\Ncommence exploration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. You haven't brought your umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha said...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Kuzuha have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just duck under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark beings always maintain\Na low body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made you some rice gruel. Try to eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:04.70,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,600)}EPISODE XI BLUE MOON RAGNAROK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you sit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real world is becoming distorted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it due to the weakened state\Nof Wicked Lord Shingan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay in bed for another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot afford to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how you tried to go out yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ended up in a sorry heap\Njust past the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, the world is banishing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine now. A night's sleep\Nhas fully restored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You are grounded until you're all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you trying to go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot answer. I have said so before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put the question to you as Dark Flame Master!\NWhere do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'll do anything\Nwith that information, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't like you going off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in secret from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But soon, all will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you perish this way\Nand leave me alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's d-d-death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be better soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were so inclined...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could use the power of Wicked Lord\NShingan to recover. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp! Do you mean that to recover...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I must feed you the black dragon\Nflower that only grows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the summit of the great dark wall\Nin the Wicked Lord's World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't provide her with a scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back or you'll catch her cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you both, but we can't have you\Ncatching her cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around, Chimera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that cold. I'm sure you have stacks\Nof homework to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spoke what must remain unspoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them the cat ate your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made several attempts to contact her\Nthrough her electro-protocol code...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she has yet to make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-oh, really? I wonder what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment Shichimiya\Nsaid she was going to make war...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought it might come down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that girl ever looked at was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was Toka who told us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just leave her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never even had a girlfriend before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MYSTERY JEWEL 298 YEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get defiant with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just being honest. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't women supposed to know\Nabout this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-how am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not chickening out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always such a busybody,\Nlike that time with Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I help you guys out when you need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want. See if I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't knock people over for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, but it's also something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are? Dekomori?!\NIt's nothing, but it's also something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?\NYou could have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ripples and magical energy were vital...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to conquer the inner me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I've conquered it for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am 100% victorious! From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I am magical devil girl\N"Spin-off Revision Plus Alpha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a game that's being\Ngradually ruined by sequels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can permanently delete\Nwhat happened earlier! Let it disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, will that do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! That'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Angel detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take what she just said seriously...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thinking, "That's good.\NShe looks like she's coping fine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean she isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she be fine?! She's acting tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've hung out with her enough\Nto know how she works!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you expect from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how they say\Nthat love is like a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a dream, you eventually wake up from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to force yourself to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? You're not my keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves Rikka, and Dekomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, and Shichimiya so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves chunibyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit jealous of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have chunibyo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I could feel the same way as all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I doubt that's how you get chunibyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you admire it means that\Nyou have a good case of chunibyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Wicked Lord Shingan\Nthe Second, Kumin-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU'VE GOT MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia, you appear to have lost your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you regain your memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna eat some medicinal plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expressly came wearing this uniform,\Nhoping it would make it easier to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tight fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have words for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words of the magician Morisummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer once fought someone\Nwho stole her identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and punished this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is when she made a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She realized how one might face and fight\None's other inner self face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One's other inner self?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You must look outwards to know thyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I found myself\Nwhen I fought my imposter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain that you, too,\Nhave an opponent to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find that opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your path will open before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a total pain. Message received?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a supply of magical energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close! Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mjolnir Hammer! Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Dark Flame Master not enough for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dare mess with\NFake Mori Summer as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha, is the moon out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lovely full moon.\NIt's going to be a blue moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blue moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya is in love with me, but I love Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. It's too complex. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero. Or rather Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you are the only suitable\Nopponent for me to fight, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way to settle the score.\NWhich means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! Devil Lord, recognized!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother. Oh, Satone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, Rikka is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only looked away for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a blue moon out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she probably realized\Nthat there's a blue moon out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, you're the one who said that\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sleeping within you would come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted it brought back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To whom I am bound by the absolute contract,\Nunchanged from long ago and for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I should travel through\Ntime and dimensions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...past the reaches of the parallel world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our contract shall continue to be binding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and by its absolute power,\Nyou will appear before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this very moment, in this world of chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world I was born into by mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I am now attempting to use\Nits powers of containment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and memory falsification,\Nto rob myself of my true memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear that in the not too distant future,\NI will pass into nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby entrust thee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the Dark Flame Dragon\Nthat dwells within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of its form,\Nwhich can plunge this world into shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power to consume\Nthis fallacious world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to revolutionize and remold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three keys are needed to revive\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, to whom I am bound by\Nthe absolute contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you indeed hold the power\Nto share my destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...surely you can assemble\Nthese three keys effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, to whom I am bound for eternity.\NI will enter a period of slumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to await that appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to endow me with power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on a future night of the blue moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this where it's hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only half-remember it,\Nbut it has to be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to dig here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Lord Shingan left this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think these are markers to\Nshow this has already been searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also searched for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't find Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key you sent into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to send a key into the past\Nis to utilize the parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your memo,\Nthe entrance to the parallel world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in the shadow cast by the 14th pylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know which pylon\Nto start counting from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she went through each and every one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. But soon, all will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, she's been doing it for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but just vaguely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember this street!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how serious you were about chunibyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how serious you were about love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you always put me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka! Rikka! Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went out looking for this\Nwhile you're sick with a cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to make it worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it said the one you are bound to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the absolute, eternal contract\Ncould bring it back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am bound to you for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find it, and prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? You don't have to do all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm supposed to be bound to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't have a single key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sophia did, so I had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, are you bound to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are bound together\Nby the absolute contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke a bone in my\Nsecond summer of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I went and buried it inside the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed at all the effort\NI went through back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody could tell where it is from that clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so hard to bury it in metal\Nthat I gave up halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess things really do stay\Nuntouched after so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the enchanted stone that\Nwill summon the Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I researched back then to find out\Nthere'd be a blue moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka. Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please do this, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, to whom I am bound for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, Ghelzonianses! This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do combat with the\NDark Flame Dragon at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally realized which opponent I must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true enemy I must fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the Dark Flame Dragon\NI loved, pursued, and gave up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the enemy with whom I must fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the opponent with whom\NI must settle my score!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ghelzonianses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who will destroy\Nthe entire world and give it new form!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to retain your magic for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe the power of my Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with your own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Flame Dragon never actually existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it could never actually be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka's cold came back with a vengeance\Nand knocked her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, I am going back in time to July 20th.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a catastrophic amount\Nof homework still looming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...summer vacation came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got too much homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll miss Yumeha growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to go visit them\Nin Jakarta as I was told to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you handling your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem is too great\Nfor the born-again Sophia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya concluded her battle\Nwith the Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and successfully\Nevolved into a new Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly has changed about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magical devil girl, for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stay unchanged,\NI needed a powerful life-changing battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to destroy the stress I had built up\Nin the name of staying unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the natural logic of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. It's the natural logic of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out to look for angels again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Say, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.97,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}TO BE CONTINUED